premise_source_doc_sentence: Lil Wayne attained his first singles chart entry in 1999 as a featured artist on Hot Boys member Juvenile 's single `` Back That Azz Up '' , which peaked at number 19 on the United States Billboard Hot 100 and became a top ten hit on the Hot R&B / Hip-Hop Songs and Hot Rap Songs charts .

The Hot Boys highly anticipated sophomore effort , Guerrilla Warfare , issued after Cash Money 's distribution deal with Universal Records , was an instant hit .
In 1996 , Lil Wayne joined the southern hip hop group Hot Boys , with his Cash Money label-mates Juvenile , Young Turk and Lil ' Doogie  (  who now goes by B.G.  )  .
Guerrilla Warfare is the second studio album by the New Orleans hip-hop group Hot Boys , released July 27 , 1999 on Cash Money Records .
